# This fixture's dependency-claim mechanism needs a real (but hand-authored,
# never `npm install`ed) node_modules/test-dep/package.json manifest — a
# declared dependency imported only by a test file must not be swallowed by
# the bin-only-dependency hazard's pre-install conservatism
# (assumption-set.md: "pre-install ... every otherwise-unreferenced
# dependency is kept alive"), which was verified empirically to keep the
# dependency fully alive (no test-only claim at all) when no node_modules is
# present. The repo-root .gitignore excludes every "node_modules/"
# directory; these two negations re-include only this fixture's own
# hand-authored one (mirrors fixtures/ts/dependency-claims/.gitignore).
!node_modules/
!node_modules/**
